explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the adoption of digital financial services (DFS) and examines the roles of financial knowledge (FK) and digital financial literacy (DFL) in this context. The research employs an online survey and ordered logistic regression for analysis. None of the provided keywords related to machine learning, deep learning, or other AI techniques are mentioned or implied in the title or abstract. The study is more aligned with behavioral economics and financial literacy research rather than computational or AI-driven methodologies.
